Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(54.24,217.44)}前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷一块面包就要坐19年牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}19 years for a loaf of bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你出狱后不到一年就会再进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My guess, you'll be back in here before another year's gone by.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时候  你就要把牢底坐穿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And next time it'll be for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远赢不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can never win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你承诺会对我好吗  菲力克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you promise you'll be good to me, Felix?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用生命承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三匹奔腾的骏马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three galloping horses
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正载着我们回到妈妈爸爸身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will be carrying us home to our mamas and papas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要走了  我们已经走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are leaving. We have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特  现在我们该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Cosette, whatever are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿好东西真不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rich pickings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我的命  你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saved my life. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德纳迪埃  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thenardier, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冉·阿让  我的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jean Valjean, my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用银餐具和这对烛台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have bought your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赎回了你的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with that silverware and these candlesticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是善的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You belong to good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看到我的40苏了吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see my 40 sous, monsieur?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚  快滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get lost! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿了我的钱  你是个臭贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got my money. You're a dirty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瑞尔威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Petit Gervais!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  我累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二  三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, there's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\t(0,1200,\blur0)\fad(3000,0)\fs35\t(200,9000,\fs45)\a10\c&H1603C0&\pos(191.4,152.1)}悲惨世界\N\N{\fs24}第一季  第二集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*如果暴政妄图统治*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Si le despotisme conspire*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*人民会奋起反抗*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Conspirons la perte des rois*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*自由*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Liberte*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*自由*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Liberte...*
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的孩子们真可爱  夫人  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You have two lovely children there, madame. - They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  虽然我不该夸自己家孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are, though I says so, I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱潘妮和阿兹玛  我的心肝宝贝  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eponine and Azelma. My pride and joy, ain't you, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你女儿也很可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you've got a lovely little one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿得这么好看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And such fine clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要坐下来  歇歇脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to come and sit down, take the weight off your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  夫人  -让你女儿跟我女儿一起玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, madame. - Look, your little girl can play with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她叫什么  -珂赛特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's her name? - Cosette.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是远道而来吗  你好像很累  -从巴黎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have you come a long way? You look ever so tired. - From Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去蒙特勒伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on my way to Montreuil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那边有很不错的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've heard there's some good work to be had there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's hubby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's... he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定历尽了艰辛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you've had a hard time of it, I dare say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一旦有了稳定的工作  就能振作起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But once I get into a steady job, I'll soon be on my feet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, of course you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这个小不点跟着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still, it's not easy holding down a job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稳定的工作可不好找  对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a little one in tow, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家旅馆是你开的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you keep the inn here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  亲爱的  德纳迪埃旅馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, that's right, dear. Thenardier's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见那招牌了吗  那是我丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See that sign there? That's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}滑铁卢中士客栈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是滑铁卢之战的英雄  救了一位上校的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was the hero of Waterloo. He saved a colonel's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背着他穿过枪林弹雨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carried him on his back through a hail of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫是军人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was your hubby a military man at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是诗人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得写诗赚不了多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a lot of money in that though, I shouldn't wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们立马就变成朋友了  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Children make friends in no time, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过路人肯定会以为她们是三姐妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you walked past that, you'd swear they were three sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我照顾一阵孩子吗  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you look after my child for a while, madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着小孩找工作  确实很难找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard to get work, especially when you have a child with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是你孤身一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, especially when you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的孩子们如此漂亮  被照管得这么好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I saw your little ones looking so pretty and well cared for,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道我来到这里是上帝的旨意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew that the good Lord had guided me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会付你钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六法郎一个月如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six francs a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-早上好  小姐  -先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good morning, mademoiselle. - Monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须七法郎才行啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll have to be seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想让我们克扣孩子的伙食费的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't want us to skimp on her meals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就给七法郎一个月  提前预支半年的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that's seven francs, six months in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在半年之内回来的  先生  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be back before then to get her, I'm sure, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话我们会把钱退你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In that case we'd of course refund you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很抱歉  规矩就是规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but those are the terms, regrettably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能搞特例  不然我们怎么开得下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't make any exceptions or where would we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七法郎六个月  一共是四十二法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six sevens, that's 42 francs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们当然还需要考虑到初始花销\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we'll have to think about initial expenses too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们象征性地收个十五法郎吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we say a nominal sum of 15 francs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五加四十二  一共五十七法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}15 and 42, that's 57 francs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五十七法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}57?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会付你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll pay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会像对亲生孩子一样好好照顾她的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will look after her and love her like your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德纳迪埃  我们早就很喜欢她了不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We love her already, don't we, Thenardier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦  我们怎么可能不喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course we do. How could we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  我跟你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Believe me, mademoiselle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的小天使在我们的照顾下会感到很幸福的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your little darling will want for nothing in our loving care,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来过来  小天使  过来和老爹玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come here, little ones. Come and play with Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你泡的茶真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, look! That's a lovely cup of tea you've got there, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特  你要做一个大姑娘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cosette, now you're to be a good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对善良的夫妇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this kind lady and gentleman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会照顾你一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will look after you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不要  -妈妈很快就回来接你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - And Maman will be back for you very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman! Maman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  请别走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-妈妈  -我会回来的  宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maman. - I'll be back, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  求求你别走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这都是为了大家好  你会懂的  -请别走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's all for the best, you'll see. - Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不能总惯着她们  对吧  -妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can't let them have all their own way, can we? - Maman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  跟妈妈说再见  -妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, bye, Maman. - Maman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  请别走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman, please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Madeleine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德林神父  如大家所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pere Madeleine, as he is known by many of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前来到了蒙特勒伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}came to Montreuil three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚到的那天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the very day he arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就冲进了一座房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he rushed into a burning house
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱出了两个孩子  救了他们的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and brought out two children, saving their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为本地带来了新产业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has brought new industry to the area
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的工厂成为了大家共同的财富源泉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and his factory has turned the fortunes of our town around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都因他更加幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are all better off because of Pere Madeleine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直是一个智慧又慷慨的雇主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has been a wise and generous employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来不把自己的利益放在大家之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ever reluctant to put himself forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  他终于接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he has at last been persuaded
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知恩图报的市民们劝说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by the grateful citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了蒙特勒伊的市长一职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to accept the office of Mayor of Montreuil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  马德林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mesdames et Messieurs, Monsieur Madeleine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Madeleine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙特勒伊的市民们  朋友们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Citizens of Montreuil, my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..I thank you for the, erm, trust that you've, you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you've shown in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝大家日安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Madeleine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了  我正在找些活干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me. I'm looking for some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  没什么好怕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. Nothing to be frightened of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine, monsieur,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀·蒂博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine Thibault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚到这里来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you are new in the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我过去在巴黎生活  -你在那里做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was living in Paris. - What work were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一家裁缝店里缝衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a seamstress at a dressmaker's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的工作也需要灵活的手指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the work here needs nimble fingers too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你觉得你能学会吗  -可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- so, you think you can learn it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您要我的话  我一定拼命干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you take me, I'll work very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不会后悔的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家庭情况是怎么样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what are your, erm, family circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我孤身一人  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am alone in the world, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有丈夫吗  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No husband? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有情人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我说过的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I said, sir, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我孤身一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀  对于你和我来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very important to me and to you, Fantine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对的诚实是非常重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you're completely honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说您为什么要关心我的生活呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why should you care about my life anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所有的工人我都关心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care about all my workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是孤身一人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..All alone in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先给你一个月的试用期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take you on a month's probation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你干得好  你会赚到钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you work well, you can prosper here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  先生  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, monsieur. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克蒂尼安太太  请带她去她的桌子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame Victurnien, will you show her to a table?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以马上开始工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you are able to begin right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-当然了  马德林先生  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, of course, Monsieur Madeleine. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就去吧  -再次感谢您  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, go now. - Thank you again, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的床头想来都是足金的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His bedhead's supposed to be solid gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕刻着天使啊翅膀啊  等等的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carved angels, wings - everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不介意在他的床上展开我的双翼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't mind spreading my wings in his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀  你得轻点  别把它弄断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be a bit gentler, Fantine. You don't want to snag it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很对  芳汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's good, Fantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开始掌握了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're getting the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  拿着  乖孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, take that. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}代笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德纳迪埃先生和太太  别来无恙...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I hope this finds you well, Monsieur and Madame Thenardier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特也一直都挺乖的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..And that my Cosette has been a good girl for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉她妈妈爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell her Maman loves her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她送上一千个吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sends her a thousand kisses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望很快就可以去领她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and hopes to be able to fetch her very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接她  应该说接她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Collect her. Collect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她给你送上一千个吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she sends you a thousand kisses. Mwah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她希望很快就可以来接她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And hopes to be able to collect her very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"您永远谦卑的..."  好家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I remain your very humble..." Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Et cetera, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,词用得真花哨  她寄钱来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very fancy language! She sent the money, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄上额外一点钱来给亲爱的小家伙买点好吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sent a bit extra to buy the dear little thing some treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That won't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她有钱能额外寄过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she's got enough to send a bit extra,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就该涨价了  该涨多少  十二法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's time to raise the rates. What do you reckon? 12 francs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  十五  我今天就写信给她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, 15. I'll write to her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以来点好吃的  德纳迪埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could do with a treat, Thenardier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就给你来点  我的小亲亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you shall get one, my little pigeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候吧  等情况好些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All in good time, when things look up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的余款都要拿去付账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any spare cash has got to go towards the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白是怎么回事  可无论我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what it is, but whatever I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像都赚不了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nothing seems to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路那头的野鸭旅店有好多客人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Wild Duck down the road gets plenty of custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这怎么就不行呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回你的角落去  加夫罗什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back in your corner, Gavroche!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  你这个小崽子  离我远点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, you little beast, and out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  德纳迪埃  真是怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know, it's a strange thing, Thenardier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直没办法喜欢上她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I've never been able to take to that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以为女儿们做任何事  但那肮脏的小东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could do anything for my girls, but that nasty little creature
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本激发不起我心中的母性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}doesn't bring any maternal instincts out in me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命盘不好  亲爱的  你做什么都没用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Born under a bad sign, love. Nothing you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  德纳迪埃  你总说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know, Thenardier, you know you said how
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这里总是很冷清  太怪了  -对  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- it's funny this place never seems to prosper? - Yes, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有考虑过  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever considered, my love,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人言可畏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that people talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如马车夫可能会说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the coachman, like, he might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去那家店  先生  德纳迪埃给啤酒掺水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Oh, don't go in there, sir, cos Thenardier waters down the beer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还附赠缺斤少两\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"And short changes you into the bargain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我常觉得你应该在门外放个标牌  写着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've often thought you could have a sign outside saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"想被骗就进来"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Come in here if you want to be swindled."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把嘴闭上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要你的建议  我会问的  懂了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I want your advice, I'll ask for it, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么看  你也想挨打吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you looking at? You want some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新警察局长来见你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the new Chief of Police is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生  我觉得我们应该认识一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire, I thought we should become acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫沙威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Javert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于昨晚抵达蒙特勒伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I arrived in Montreuil last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐  督察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please take a seat, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想喝一杯吗  -不了  谢谢  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can I offer you a drink? - No, thank you, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我  这是您偏好的称呼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, is that how you prefer to be addressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听过别人称呼您为马德林神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have heard you called Pere Madeleine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  市长先生就可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Monsieur le Maire will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的这个工厂非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a fine establishment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说您通过雇佣所有想工作的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am told you have restored the prosperity of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重振了这个城镇的繁荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by giving employment to all those who are willing to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  这里的犯罪很少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consequently, there's very little crime here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我愿意这样相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I like to think that that is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是贼偷东西不是因为他又穷又绝望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But a thief does not steal because he is poor and desperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他偷东西因为他有犯罪心理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he steals because he has a criminal mentality,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是堕落的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he is degenerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单地说  因为他是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he is, to put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得说我们意见相左\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there I have to tell you that we disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信我们中的大多数人可善可恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe most of us are capable of good and evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们成为什么样子取决于境遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how we turn out depends on our circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们受到的对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how we are treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个结论是您根据自身经验得出的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And has your own experience led you to that conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待今后就此话题更多地探讨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I look forward to many interesting discussions on this topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在  我作为警察局长向您保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now, let me assure you that as your Chief of Police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将尽我所能地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shall do everything in my power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出  逮捕并惩罚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to seek out, apprehend and punish
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的城镇中的每一个犯罪者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}every single wrong-doer in your fine town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴听到这个  警督\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Glad to hear it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你在蒙特勒伊的任务不会太艰巨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think your task won't be too demanding here in Montreuil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗略检查之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On cursory inspection,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的市民看起来满足并守序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your citizens seem to be contented and well ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样野心勃勃的人为什么要选择这样的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, why does an ambitious man choose a posting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您推断我有野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You deduce that I am ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开监狱系统后  我全身心投入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since I left the Prison Service, I have dedicated myself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅追捕明显的罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to pursuing not only the obvious offences,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些藏起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the hidden ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是当下的罪犯  还有以前的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not only in the present, but in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候一个人可能看起来成功富有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes a man may be seen to be rich, successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品行端正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}prosperous, virtuous...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而同时他可能隐藏着一个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..While all the time he may be harbouring a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的丑恶行径\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something rotten in his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该让这种秘密隐藏下去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it right that such a secret should remain hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该让这种人继续享受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it right that such a man should continue to enjoy the fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不为人知的罪恶的成果吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of his wickedness undiscovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为这个城镇里有这种人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think there is such a man here in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人到处都是  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are such men everywhere, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我的工作才如此迷人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what makes my work so fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  必须得有无可争议的证据证明他有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, one must have incontrovertible proof of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这需要时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想占用你宝贵的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't want to keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-认识你是我的荣幸  -我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's been a pleasure to make your acquaintance. - Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想  跟你交谈时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I've been thinking, as we've talked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我想起了一个我曾经熟识的一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you remind me of someone I used to know rather well at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他偷了一个孩子的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He stole from a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未为自己的罪行付出过代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never paid for his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在想不起他的名字了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't recall his name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, well. Goodnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不敢相信他没邀请我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still can't believe he didn't invite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-范范会邀请你的  不是吗  范比  -闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fabs would, wouldn't you, Fabby? - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人去过那吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has anyone ever been up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我打赌他会让芳汀进  -为什么会让我进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I bet he'd let Fantine in though. - Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他喜欢你  我们都看见他看你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cos he likes you and we've seen him looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我猜他会让你进他房间  -让你上他的床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I bet he'd let you in his room. - Let you in his bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-如果他要求做  你会就范吗  -不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you, if he asked? - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  别装了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, hoity-toity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那是什么  芳汀  挺漂亮的  -没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's that, Fantine? That's pretty. - It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧  范范  是只小鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Fabs, it's a little bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, that is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给谁做的  -没谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who's it for? - No-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心  薇琪过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look out, Vicky's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要你做这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who told you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没谁  夫人  但我的任务已经完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No-one, madame, but I'd finished my quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务做完了也不能在这自娱自乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not here to amuse yourself when you finish your quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-应该接新任务来做  -抱歉  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You ask for more work. - Sorry, madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我真想当场解雇你  -请不要解雇我  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've a good mind to dismiss you on the spot. - Please, no, madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后警告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Consider this a final warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的老贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nasty old bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我知道你和我们一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I know your little girl's health and happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关心你女儿是否健康快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"is as dear to you as it is to my dear wife and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一小笔"  一小笔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"A trifling sum..." A trifling sum?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙写得真可恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This fellow writes abominably.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"只需一小笔钱  每月15法郎"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"A trifling sum of 15 francs a month."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每月15法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}15 francs a month?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.55,0:24:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这么多钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't pay that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想不想听后面的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to hear the rest or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们希望尽快收到这笔钱"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"We expect to receive this money due to us very promptly."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}代笔人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说她是个妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was some kind of a prostitute, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.12,0:24:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢说别人坏话  但是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't like to speak ill of anyone, but, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.67,0:24:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这小女孩肯定是罪恶的果实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and no doubt the little girl was conceived in sin
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了她的累赘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and had become some sort of encumbrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用想就知道  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't bear thinking about, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.69,0:24:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人过的都是不正常的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These people don't lead natural lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.68,0:24:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能现在都把自己女儿忘干净了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's probably forgotten all about the little girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在写信给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She still writes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  时不时吧  她想起来就写\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah, I mean, now and then, when she thinks about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.98,0:24:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"希望你好好照顾她"  之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I hope you're looking after her proper", and all that, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.77,0:24:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对我们还有这个小姑娘有什么用呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but what good is that to us or the little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.44,0:25:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.30,0:25:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们被利用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..You have been taken advantage of.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right there, madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想留宿一两晚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you thinking of staying a night or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.15,0:25:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面有间不错的房间  现在没有人住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a lovely room on the front that's vacant just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经在野鸭旅店住下了  马夫推荐的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've taken a room at the Wild Duck. The coachman recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.46,0:25:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是滑铁卢战役中的英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was one of the heroes of Waterloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.00,0:25:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿破仑亲自授予了我荣誉军团勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was awarded the Legion d'Honneur by Napoleon himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想看看吗  -不用了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you care to examine it? - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.30,0:25:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不了吗  好吧  -祝安  谢谢你的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No... yeah. - Good day to you. Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.37,0:25:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可悲的老女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miserable old cow, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.80,0:25:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我倒霉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tant pis!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.65,0:25:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.36,0:25:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿破仑万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vive Napoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿破仑·波拿巴对法国的伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Napoleon Bonaparte did more harm to France
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.92,0:25:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比英国  俄国和奥地利的军队加起来还要大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than all the armies of Britain, Russia and Austria combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听  就是一个野蛮人  一个粗人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hear, hear. A barbarian, a savage,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.95,0:25:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢上帝  现在他是个遭人鄙视的流犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and thanks be to God, now a despised exile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这位年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But here is a young man
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.62,0:26:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着正确的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who thinks in the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.30,0:26:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.12,0:26:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的孙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my grandson...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.28,0:26:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马吕斯·彭眉胥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Marius Pontmercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.33,0:26:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿破仑就是一个卖国贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Napoleon was a traitor to his country
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.14,0:26:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲也是一个卖国贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and my father was a traitor to his country too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.23,0:26:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唾弃他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spit upon them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.60,0:26:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王万岁  法国万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vive le Roi! Vive la France!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.72,0:26:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王万岁  法国万岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vive le Roi! Vive la France!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.62,0:26:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.58,0:26:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  这封信刚刚寄到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur, this letter has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.71,0:26:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.26,0:26:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it seems your father
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经离死不远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is on his deathbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.56,0:26:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, what do you say... to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.05,0:27:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很好  -哈哈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good! - Ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.70,0:27:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.20,0:27:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.42,0:27:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以离开了  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, off you go, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.00,0:27:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  这男孩应该去见父亲最后一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The boy should see his father before he dies, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.01,0:27:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是理所应当的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.12,0:27:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他想去  我不会阻止他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't forbid it, if he wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.43,0:27:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.34,0:27:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不去  你会后悔一辈子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't, you might be sorry your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.28,0:27:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我陪你去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.24,0:27:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Women!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.70,0:27:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不爱  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to love them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.67,0:28:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是个骗子  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a liar, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.76,0:28:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生  快来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire, come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.19,0:28:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-马德林先生  -夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Monsieur Madeleine! - Madame...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.93,0:28:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-先生  别  -我必须得去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Monsieur... No, please! - No, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.07,0:28:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur! Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.90,0:28:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.88,0:28:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这车卸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unload that cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.51,0:28:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把马牵好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Control that horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.40,0:28:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人把马给松开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone untether the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.55,0:28:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.82,0:28:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住  康斯特布尔  我们会救你出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on, Constable, we'll get you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.51,0:28:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找人帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get someone to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.80,0:28:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来得20分钟  等人来他都被压死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's 20 minutes from here. He'll be crushed to death by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.55,0:28:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都在这了  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all in hand, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.67,0:28:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.83,0:29:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.61,0:29:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有影响力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most instructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.85,0:29:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有多人见证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And witnessed by so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.85,0:29:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马德林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Madeleine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.55,0:29:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.26,0:29:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个伤风败俗女子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This immoral young woman
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.83,0:29:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这家工厂  这个小镇的耻辱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a disgrace to the factory and the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.67,0:30:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是真的  我是无辜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not true. I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.85,0:30:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉  先生  她比妓女好不到哪去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I regret to say, monsieur, she is no better than a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.47,0:30:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有个私生子  还把孩子丢在蒙费梅伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She has a bastard child, she abandoned at Montfermeil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.59,0:30:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没抛弃她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}....I never abandoned her!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.81,0:30:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没抛弃她  我每月都寄十五法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never abandoned her. I send 15 francs per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.51,0:30:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我一半的工资还多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than half my wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.47,0:30:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的小婊子  你真丢人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lying little whore. You're a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.99,0:30:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生  相信我  珂赛特是我的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire, believe me. My Cosette is all I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.75,0:30:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的小婊子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lying little whore!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.55,0:30:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她上班是就在做这个事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what she does when she's supposed to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.54,0:30:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给她小杂种的玩具  -相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A toy for her little bastard. - Believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.55,0:30:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  你们两个  够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough, both of you! Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.71,0:30:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀·蒂博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine Thibault?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.19,0:30:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.59,0:30:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我问过你的家庭情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember I asked you about your family
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.78,0:30:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你在世上孤身一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you said you were alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.02,0:30:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要是我跟你说了我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought if I told you about my little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.86,0:30:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会解雇我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'd turn me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.65,0:30:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.40,0:30:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又没什么坏处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was no harm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.39,0:30:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我那时怕你  -别听她的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was frightened of you. - Don't listen to her, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.06,0:30:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她就是个淫妇  -我不是  我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's an immoral woman. - I am not! I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.57,0:30:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但孩子是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the child is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.18,0:30:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这有罪吗  -她抛弃了她的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that a crime? - And she abandoned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.30,0:31:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.93,0:31:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请相信我  -我无法相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Please believe me. - I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.94,0:31:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被开除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.35,0:31:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还能去干什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.35,0:31:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有50法郎  我建议你离开这里  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's 50 francs. I advise you to leave the town, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能走  我还欠别人钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can't leave this town. I owe people money here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.31,0:31:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去找别的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, find some other employment!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.76,0:31:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都说你是位善良的好心人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They said that you were a kind and good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.19,0:31:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也以为你是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.87,0:31:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实不然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.45,0:31:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.06,0:31:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-恶魔  -够了  够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A monster! - That's enough! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.00,0:31:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎敢侮辱我们好心的马德林神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you insult our good Pere Madeleine?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.84,0:31:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.54,0:31:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.52,0:32:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.77,0:32:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾  驾  别慌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on! Come on! Steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.59,0:32:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H3123E9&\b1\pos(187.2,151.92)}巴黎警察局总部
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.68,0:33:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总督察  我叫沙威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chief Inspector, my name is Javert.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.88,0:33:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚接管蒙特勒伊地区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have just taken charge in Montreuil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.40,0:33:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威探长  你来巴黎干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inspector Javert, what are you doing in Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.89,0:33:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现了一名危险的罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've identified a dangerous criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.19,0:33:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我前来与您商议如何处置此人  -他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've come to consult you on how to proceed. - Who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.57,0:33:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫冉·阿让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His name is Jean Valjean.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.82,0:33:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年前我在土伦监狱认识了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew him years ago at the prison hulks at Toulon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.72,0:33:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出狱后不久就偷窃孩童财物并逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He stole from a child within days of his release and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.05,0:33:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个力大又残忍的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A man of exceptional strength and brutality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.59,0:33:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今他在外假扮成蒙特勒伊市长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's now posing as the Mayor of Montreuil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.31,0:33:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.15,0:33:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总督察  我认识此人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tell you, I know the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.81,0:33:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冉·阿让已被拘留\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jean Valjean is in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.12,0:33:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天前他在阿伊勒欧克洛谢被捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was arrested four days ago in Ailly-le-Haut-Clocher.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.58,0:33:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时将会接受审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In due course, he will stand trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人承认自己是冉·阿让了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has this man confessed to being Jean Valjean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.97,0:33:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有  但他会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not yet, but he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.21,0:34:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-已经有人指认他了  -但是先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He has been identified. - But monsieur...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.07,0:34:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住  对公众人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And bear in mind, it's a very serious matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.14,0:34:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出指控是非常严重的一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}making accusations against important public figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.15,0:34:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建议你多加小心  沙威探长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd advise you to be more careful, Inspector Javert.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.53,0:35:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Evening, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.66,0:36:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mon pere?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.50,0:36:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.16,0:36:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.79,0:36:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你是彭眉胥男爵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will be Baron Pontmercy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.98,0:36:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿破仑亲自在滑铁卢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The honour was bestowed on me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.61,0:36:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,授予我这项荣誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by Napoleon himself at Waterloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.68,0:36:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今由你继承\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it is yours by right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.01,0:36:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.04,0:36:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫德纳迪埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Called Thenardier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.88,0:36:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.81,0:36:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你今后遇见他  尽你所能款待他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ever meet him, do the best, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.84,0:37:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz17.08\org(18.72,296.64)\frx16\fry358\pos(176.16,122.4)}芳汀\N蒙特勒伊克拉佩小街
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.16,0:37:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子感染了粟疹热病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The child has caught a miliary fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.82,0:37:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.74,0:37:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们需要钱买药  40法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're asking for money for medicine. 40 francs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.46,0:37:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可怜的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My poor child.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.03,0:37:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不把你女儿接到这来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not go and fetch your daughter here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.70,0:37:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她和我一起过这悲惨的生活吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And have her share my wretched life?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.53,0:37:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想令她蒙羞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to bring shame on her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.53,0:37:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在这样就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's better off where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.58,0:38:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但天晓得我要去哪赚钱供她留在那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Though God knows how I'll find the money for her keep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.69,0:38:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个非常美丽的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..You're a very pretty young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.92,0:38:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而漂亮女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's always ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.07,0:38:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that a pretty young woman can...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.94,0:38:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到生计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..Make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.38,0:38:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你明白我的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.63,0:38:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您晚安  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bonsoir, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又买又卖  今夜我又买又卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm buying and I'm selling, I'm selling and I'm buying tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.29,0:39:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你没有头发和牙齿  你能改变自己的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're bald and toothless, you can change your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.23,0:39:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜我又买又卖  女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm selling and I'm buying tonight, ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.17,0:39:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有闪闪金发  也有乌亮黑发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got golden, I've got glossy black,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有卷发  有直发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got curly, I've got straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.89,0:39:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有长发  有短发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got long and I've got short.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.61,0:39:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  摸摸这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, have a feel of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.47,0:39:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是如丝绸般柔软\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that soft as silk?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.43,0:39:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有牙齿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.52,0:39:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不想今晚带着一口亮丽的新牙回家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you like to go home tonight with a lovely new set of teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.63,0:39:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们手头的东西可以在我这抵一些价钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll take what you've got in part exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.57,0:39:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更公平的了  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't say fairer than that now, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了一位美人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I say, there's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.18,0:39:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让路  女士们  让她过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make way, ladies. Let her come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.39,0:39:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.70,0:40:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好久都没见过一头这么美的秀发了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that is as lovely a head of hair as I've seen in a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.22,0:40:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全放下来看看  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let it all down, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.07,0:40:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要卖吗  -多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you selling, dear? - How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.26,0:40:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-十法郎  -只有这么点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ten francs. - Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.39,0:40:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最高价了  随你在哪也卖不了更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the top rate. You won't get more anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.66,0:40:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你能考虑舍弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you was thinking of parting
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.35,0:40:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些亮丽的白牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with those lovely white teeth, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.47,0:40:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要前面两颗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the two front ones even.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.14,0:40:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能给你两个拿破仑金币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could give you two Napoleons for those.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.39,0:40:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值40法郎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}40 francs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.18,0:40:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有牙一起50\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}50 altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.74,0:40:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要五分钟就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just five minutes' work.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.66,0:40:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意下如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.51,0:40:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.99,0:41:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍事休息  女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A short intermission, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.43,0:41:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.51,0:41:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在那坐下  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit yourself down there, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.66,0:41:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.62,0:41:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.78,0:41:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.83,0:41:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个  母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at this, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.03,0:41:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么好的货色  我们可不经常遇见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't often see anything as good as this, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.51,0:41:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你想好了要做这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, you quite sure you want to go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.26,0:41:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还可以改变心意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're allowed to change your mind, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.59,0:42:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.62,0:42:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.74,0:42:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快剪完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it. Nearly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.14,0:42:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了  母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goody good, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.55,0:42:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我相信它很快又会长回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There. It'll soon grow again, I dare say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.62,0:42:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我把她按住  母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, help me hold her still, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.11,0:43:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.62,0:43:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一枚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.26,0:43:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shh, it's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.07,0:43:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才像话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.87,0:43:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定很有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She must be rolling in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.83,0:43:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们要的还不够多  你说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think we've been asking for enough, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.78,0:43:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的小女孩正生命垂危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The poor little girl's at death's door
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.59,0:43:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亟待医生的救治  你觉得该要多少钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the doctor's demanding, what do you reckon?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.51,0:43:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-100法郎  -好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 100? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.26,0:44:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续  好好擦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on, do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.26,0:44:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我们恳求你能为小珂赛特竭尽所能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"We beg that you do all you can for little Cosette.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.43,0:44:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德纳迪埃"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thenardier."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.74,0:44:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们我会尽快寄钱过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them I'll send it as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.11,0:44:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么筹钱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how are you going to raise the money, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.95,0:44:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卖掉了头发和牙齿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've sold my hair and my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.18,0:44:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该会继续把剩下的也卖掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might as well get on with it and sell the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.07,0:44:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, mademoiselle...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.83,0:44:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真可惜  -你也这么觉得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What a shame. - You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.78,0:44:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞错了方向  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've gone about it the wrong way round, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.07,0:44:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该在卖掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have gone on the game
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.55,0:44:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一头秀发和亮丽白牙之前就加入行当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before you sold your pretty hair and your lovely white teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.14,0:44:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在这个样子  谁还会要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's going to take you, looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.91,0:45:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.51,0:46:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀  是你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.66,0:46:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.59,0:46:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-芳汀  -别管她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fantine. - Leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.74,0:46:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  女士们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Evening, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.78,0:46:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-多么美好的夜晚  -的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Lovely night for it. - Indeed it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.47,0:46:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.39,0:46:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have we got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.07,0:46:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好惊悚啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.83,0:46:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收费多少  秃子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how much do you charge, baldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.39,0:46:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得值多少钱就收多少  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you think it's worth, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.22,0:46:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我觉得一文不值呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about nothing, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.39,0:46:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听到了吗  先生们  一文不值怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hear that, gentlemen? How about nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.35,0:46:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是一文不值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all she's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.41,0:46:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我得生活  先生  就像你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have to live, monsieur, the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.66,0:46:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一样吗  你这厚颜无耻的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same as me? You cheeky cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.14,0:47:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听说过这样的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you ever hear the like of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.59,0:47:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我这么做是为了找乐子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I do this for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.35,0:47:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了养活我的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do it to feed my little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.66,0:47:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要是不想跟我做生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if you don't want business,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.22,0:47:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请行行好...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do me a favour...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.83,0:47:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.11,0:47:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甘受责备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stand rebuked.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.18,0:47:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I humbly beg your pardon, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.51,0:47:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你叫什么名字  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might I ask your name, mademoiselle?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.59,0:47:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫芳汀  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.35,0:47:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  芳汀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bonsoir, Fantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.07,0:47:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能原谅我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I hope I am forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.47,0:47:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bonsoir, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.66,0:47:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀  送你个东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine, something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.22,0:48:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.70,0:48:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.74,0:48:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一种不能容忍的暴行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is an outrage that cannot be tolerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.59,0:48:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个受人尊敬的拥有财产的公民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A respectable property-owning citizen
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.91,0:48:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个妓女袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}attacked by a common prostitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.91,0:48:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把这个娼妓关进牢房  -遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take this whore to the cells. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.15,0:48:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被判刑六个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.14,0:48:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六个月吗  我的孩子怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months? But what about my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.74,0:48:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不关我的事  把她带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's no concern of mine. Take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.62,0:48:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  沙威先生  我不是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, Monsieur Javert! I wasn't always like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.55,0:48:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本是个好女孩...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.52,0:48:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她带走  她身上散发着堕落的恶臭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take her away! She stinks of degradation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.39,0:48:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.78,0:48:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.14,0:48:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.39,0:48:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住她  你们这些笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seize her, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.47,0:48:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看到这个男人了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see this man here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.35,0:48:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这个被你们称为市长先生的魔鬼了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see this monster here that you call Monsieur le Maire?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.62,0:48:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.95,0:48:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该是个好人  看看他都干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's supposed to be so good. What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.87,0:49:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把我扔到街上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He threw me out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.66,0:49:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道为什么吗  因为我想照顾我的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you know why? Because I tried to care for my little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.51,0:49:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔鬼市长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monster of a mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.07,0:49:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生是魔鬼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire, a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.62,0:49:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在明白了  可以放我走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You understand now. You'll let me go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.07,0:49:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做个安分的妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be a good little whore now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.39,0:49:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可以对我为所欲为  我不会抱怨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can do what they like with me and I won't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.18,0:49:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想工作养活我的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I want is to be able to work to feed my child
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.91,0:49:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她从蒙费梅伊接回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and fetch her from Montfermeil.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.51,0:49:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  我...我不能呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, I can't... I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.83,0:49:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请感受一下  -滚开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Feel it. - Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.70,0:49:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我来照顾她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! I will take her into my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.11,0:49:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无权这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have no right!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.99,0:49:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芳汀  我不该赶你走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fantine, I was wrong to dismiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.55,0:49:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.11,0:49:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许为时已晚  但请让我弥补一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps it's too late, but let me try to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.31,0:49:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你还债  找到你的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll, I'll pay your debts, I'll find your child
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.13,0:49:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that you can be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.87,0:49:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用再工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need never work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.99,0:49:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会照顾你  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take care of you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.51,0:49:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.83,0:50:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在开玩笑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.51,0:50:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在带你去医院  来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let me take you to the infirmary. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.03,0:50:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跟我走  -不  我不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come with me. - No, I forbid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.59,0:50:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人被判刑了  她得去坐牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This woman has been sentenced then she is going to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.70,0:50:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把她带去牢房  -别碰她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take her to the cells. - Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.95,0:50:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙威先生  在市政事务上  我的级别高于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Javert, in municipal matters, I outrank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.43,0:50:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我警告你  别在此事上跟我过不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I warn you, don't cross me over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.87,0:50:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人对你来说到底意味着什么  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What exactly does this woman mean to you, Monsieur le Maire?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.51,0:50:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是需要我帮助的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone who needs my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.95,0:50:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个娼妓吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A common whore?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.26,0:50:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是低人一等的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is the lowest of the low.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.03,0:50:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要冒着名誉风险去帮助这样一个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would risk your good name to help a creature like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.78,0:50:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是是上帝的造物  沙威先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's one of God's creatures, Monsieur Javert,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.31,0:50:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她虽然毫无过错却经受了如此大的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she has suffered grievously through no fault of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.95,0:50:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我伤害了她  所以现在我要设法补救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I injured her myself, and now I want to make amends if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.39,0:50:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我无话可说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You astonish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.07,0:51:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你不要挡着我的路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now stand out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.03,0:51:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿干吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.83,0:51:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.66,0:51:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在为你祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm praying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.39,0:51:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.70,0:51:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能请你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.79,0:52:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人把我的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..send for my daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.87,0:52:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珂赛特找来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cosette, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.59,0:52:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.62,0:52:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要的话我可以亲自去找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If necessary, I'll go for her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.03,0:52:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我曾是个罪人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been a...a sinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.39,0:52:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果珂赛特在我身边的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when I have Cosette with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.22,0:52:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..it will mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.70,0:52:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝已经原谅我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that God has forgiven me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.47,0:52:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生  沙威督察来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inspector Javert is here, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.18,0:52:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐吧  督察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit down, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.26,0:53:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的好意  市长先生  我更想站着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Monsieur le Maire. I prefer to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.62,0:53:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请便  你来意是为何啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you wish. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.35,0:53:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来检举一位警官所犯下的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have come to report a serious misdemeanour
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.62,0:53:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分严重的罪行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by an officer of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.26,0:53:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一位警官呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.51,0:53:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.47,0:53:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是前来辞任的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have come to offer my resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.70,0:53:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.03,0:53:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  我想为我早些时候的行为道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Firstly, I'd like to apologise for my conduct earlier and...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.43,0:53:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在巴黎警察总署当众侮辱了您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I denounced you to police headquarters in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.55,0:53:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还错误的怀疑您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suspected you, wrongly as it turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.95,0:53:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个臭名昭著的重罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be a notorious felon,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.18,0:53:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我曾经的24601号囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}once known to me as Prisoner Number 24601.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.83,0:53:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个叫冉·阿让的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A man named Jean Valjean.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.83,0:53:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.26,0:53:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.74,0:53:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.62,0:53:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.31,0:53:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么改变主意了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What made you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.07,0:54:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市长先生  真正的阿让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur le Maire, the real Valjean...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.47,0:54:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.95,0:54:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.22,0:54:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将因多项指控在阿拉斯的法庭接受审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's about to stand trial in Arras for a number of offences,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.99,0:54:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中包括从一个叫小瑞尔威的孩子那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}including the theft of a coin from a child
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.47,0:54:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窃取硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who went by the name of Petit Gervais.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.31,0:54:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瑞尔威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Petit Gervais?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.26,0:54:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瑞尔威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Petit Gervais.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.59,0:54:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您对这个名字耳熟吗  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does the name mean anything to you, Monsieur le Maire?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.03,0:54:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人认罪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has this man confessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.51,0:54:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.18,0:54:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他的谎言一定会在法庭上被揭穿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but no doubt his lies will be exposed in court
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.18,0:54:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他将会被判处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he'll be sentenced to penal servitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.07,0:54:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服终身苦役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.62,0:54:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's over for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.91,0:54:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审判就在明天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trial is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.83,0:54:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚会乘马车去阿拉斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take the coach to Arras tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.66,0:55:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将会是我作为巡官所履行的最后职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that will be my last duty as Police Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.99,0:55:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodnight, Monsieur le Maire.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.79,0:55:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗  嬷嬷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can I do for you, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.83,0:55:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的病人  芳汀·蒂博  那个娼妓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our patient, Fantine Thibault, the prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.14,0:55:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么叫她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't call her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.87,0:55:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生让我告诉您  她现在很虚弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doctor wanted you to know that she... She's very weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.14,0:55:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该时日无多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She has very little time left on this Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.43,0:55:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她一直在念叨希望见到她的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she speaks constantly of seeing her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.95,0:55:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.62,0:56:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说如果她想在死前见到她的孩子的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doctor says if she is to see her child
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.79,0:56:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子得立刻...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before she dies, the child should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.43,0:56:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我知道了  嬷嬷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I understand, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.87,0:56:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我的失礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.26,0:56:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  嬷嬷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.55,0:56:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽你所能去帮她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please do your best for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.55,0:56:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有其他要做的事  失陪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now there are things that I have to attend to. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.59,0:56:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿了  对不对  你拿了我的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got it, haven't you? You've got my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.79,0:57:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个臭贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a dirty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.03,0:57:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A curse on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.47,0:58:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克蒂尼安太太  马德林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame Victurnien. Monsieur Madeleine!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.59,0:58:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事麻烦你  如果你愿意帮忙的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have an errand for you, if you'd be so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.03,0:58:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你记得芳汀·蒂博吗  -我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You remember Fantine Thibault? - Indeed I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.59,0:58:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她住院了  她现在病得很重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's in hospital, she's very ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.39,0:58:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你去蒙费梅伊找到她的小女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to go to Montfermeil and fetch her little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.14,0:58:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.66,0:58:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我想自己去的  但我还要去其他地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd go myself, but I... There's somewhere else I have to be.

